      "markdown": "# 中考满分作文背诵\n\n## Great changes in my hometown \n\nEa and poor town.Mostof ppe were frmer.There were f factories.The pepledeoug foodoat andorolt a hard life.\n\n\n\nGreat changes have taken place in the past twenty years.The people have found a lot of ways of making mony.Now there ae many tau buildings.They are very beautiful.Roads are wide and clean.People can take buses or drive their town cars to go to work.Many people have cell phones und personal computers.Peoples living conditions have improved a lot.Thmks to the government's efforts.My hometown is becoming more and more a E beautitul.\n\n## [译文]在我的家乡发生了很大的变化\n\na 二十多年来，我的家乡只是个又老又穷的小镇。大多数人都是农民。有几个\n\n在过去的二十年，发生了巨大的变化。人们已经发现很多的赚钱途径。现在有许多高大的建筑物，他们很漂亮。道路宽阔，又干净。人们可以塔公车或驾驶自己的汽车上班。许多人有手机和个人电脑。人民的生活条件有了很大的进步。由于政府的努力，我的家乡正变得越来越美丽。",
